text: Chyba is a surname. Notable people with this name include: *Andrew Chyba, Green party candidate for South Wales West in 2011 National Assembly for Wales election *Christopher Chyba, American astrobiologist *Jiří Chyba, Czech paracyclist, competed in 2011 UCI Para-cycling Track World Championships – Men's individual pursuit *Monique Chyba (born 1969), control theorist at the University of Hawaii *Pavel Chyba, Czech fisher, winner of 2010 World Fly Fishing Championships ==See also== *7923 Chyba, an asteroid named after Christopher Chyba *Chiba (surname) *Chiba (disambiguation)
